{"id":241674,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-西安七旬老翁护地上访被政府官员施暴-图/","date":"2012-07-22T10:31:08Z","modified":"2012-07-22T10:31:08Z","title":"维权网 | 西安七旬老翁护地上访被政府官员施暴 (图)","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>维权网信息员吴法效报道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)7<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>18<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">下午</span>3</span><span>时许，西安市灞桥区洪庆街道办事处田王村村民王性善、王满祥因不满自己的承包地被地方政府（无国家建设用地规划批文）违规违法占用，赴西安市国土灞桥分局信访，后到街道办面谈，遭到接待的工作人员群殴。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>按照国土灞桥分局主管信访工作负责人的安排去找洪庆街道办事处面谈为宜，主持接待的是该街办土地监察所付所长王宏伟（曾用名；王锁），在数小时的接待中，身为该街办土地监察所付所长该街办土地监察所付所长王宏伟（曾用名；王锁）不顾自己公务员身份出言不逊，只是重复一句话“我看、你们还是回去算了”。为此引发七旬老翁的强烈不满，王性善、王满祥两人也不予以接受因而发生争执，此刻该街办土地监察所付所长王宏伟（曾用名；王锁）脸色大变，说；“给你个好脸色还认不得你，我看你是想挨打了”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>时许，王宏伟纠集洪庆街道办事处数十名工作人员起哄而上施暴群殴，将王性善、王满祥二人打倒在地，并拳脚相加，而该街办门卫人员还利用电线等物抽打两位上访人，导致王性善老人左大腿面部、右胳膊小肘外侧紫青於肿痛苦难耐，时至今日无人问津。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王宏伟（曾用名；王锁）身为政府工作人员公然违法殴打前来上访民众，侵犯了公民人身安全与信访权利，应该受到法律的惩治。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王性善电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13572465317</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fInrBRyOnSQ/UAu6XOc20OI/AAAAAAAAJiw/es18qfX5cVs/s1600/IMG_1096.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fInrBRyOnSQ/UAu6XOc20OI/AAAAAAAAJiw/es18qfX5cVs/s320/IMG_1096.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>被殴打致伤的王性善老人</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Tj6VHaeIzb8/UAu67miyXNI/AAAAAAAAJjA/h2lVSM0AfIc/s1600/IMG_1097.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Tj6VHaeIzb8/UAu67miyXNI/AAAAAAAAJjA/h2lVSM0AfIc/s320/IMG_1097.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1985472191423614258?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/c84add9aIMG_1096.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}